title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Jun 17 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Jun 17 2022
description:
Clay opens the show by saying that the Biden Recession has already begun. Montage of Biden campaigning on ending fossil fuels. Buck says, "Can Biden make it any more clear that he hates the fossil fuel industry -- at least when he wants Democrat votes?" Biden lies about inflation, competency seems lower, Clay says, every time we hear new audio. Moderate Elon Musk drives the Blue Checks mad. Kamala Harris to head task force on "online harassment."

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
